dialogue.text:
Hey, some dude that plays music wants to talk to you. I think he's further in. Some of the doors are blocked, but I'm sure you'll figure it out! 
 Just so you know, you can press 'ESC' to quit at any time.
I was told me not to be too nice, so I can't really help you... Speaking to every purple ghost you see could help you out though.

dialogue 0.text: Try bumping into these ghosts over here. See how they react according to their color? Green moves right, and purple moves down.

dialogue 2.text: If ever you get stuck, just speak to any of the ghosts to fix the situation.

dialogue 1.text: If you want to go further in, just try to reach that red carpet over there. These ghosts might try to get in your way though.

dialogue 0.text: This puzzle on the right is pretty hard to solve... I think I know what to do though. Would you like me to give you some hints?

dialogue 1.text: You might want to write this down.

dialogue 3.text:
Let's call the three ghosts on the far right wall, from top to bottom, '1', '2', and '3'. 
 I think you need to start on the left side of the group, near the bottom of the room. Then you need to push your way to the bottom right, touching only 1 ghost on the way, before you touch '3' from the bottom.

dialogue 4.text: Then you slowly make your way out of the group of ghosts where you came, and move around them to the top right. From there I'm sure you can figure out what to do! If you get trapped by the ghosts, just talk to one of them.

dialogue 0.text: I remember one night, when it was real dark, my love and I were trying to sleep. I kept tracing words on her back, and she told me she didn't know what I was spelling out.

dialogue 1.text:
'I think I'm in love with you.' 
 That's what I wrote.

dialogue.text:
Christmas ?!? 
 What's that ?! 
 My calendar only says '310 days left till Halloween'!
